# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Root .gitignore — medication-reminder (ASP.NET Core + Angular)
# Protects secrets and build artifacts regardless of subtree.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# === Secrets / credentials (NEVER commit) ===
**/appsettings.secrets.json
**/appsettings.Local.json
**/secrets.json
*.pfx
*.p12
*.key
*.pem
.env
.env.*
# NuGet API keys / user secrets
*.nuget.config.local
secrets.*

# === OS files ===
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# === IDE / editors ===
.idea/
.vs/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.user
*.suo
*.userprefs

# === .NET / ASP.NET build artifacts ===
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/artifacts/
*.dll
*.pdb
*.exe
TestResults/
project.lock.json

# === Angular / Node ===
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.angular/cache
**/tmp/
**/out-tsc/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-error.log
**/coverage/

# === Logs ===
*.log
**/Logs/
